snippet.title: Phantom Crash: Blue Skies Bring Tears - Official Trailer 2
snippet.description:
This is the second trailer of Phantom Crash that I created.  That time wasn't great as I didn't even receive the final logo print in time to include in the trailer, but all was still good anyway.

Funnily enough, I think this was the fouth video I've created.  Heh, I guess I was getting better.  Gosh, my skills sure came a long way since then.
